/*********************************************************************************************\
 * Prometheus support
 *
 * The text format for metrics, labels and values is documented at [1]. Only
 * the UTF-8 text encoding is supported.
 *
 * [1]
 * https://github.com/prometheus/docs/blob/master/content/docs/instrumenting/exposition_formats.md
 *
